<section id="about">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="content">
      <div class="main-content">
        <h2 class="section-heading">ABOUT ME</h2>
        <h3>FULLSTACK DEVELOPER</h3>
        <p>
          I am a passionate web developer with a love for building innovative
          and user-friendly applications. My expertise lies creating web
          applications on both the frontend and backend. I am especially
          experienced in using tools such as Javascript, Typescript, React,
          Node.js, Express.js, Postgresql, MongoDB and so on. I am a Computer
          Science graduate from Babcock University in Nigeria and am currently
          working on gaining a masters degree in Software Engineering at the
          University of Hertfordshire, UK. The most important thing for me is
          always learning and improving my skills.
        </p>
        <p>
          I enjoy programming, building applications and working with new
          technologies.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="image">
        <img src="/images/profilepic.jpg" alt="avatar" />
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <style>
    section {
      background-color: var(--clr-neutral-900);
      padding-block: 6rem;
    }

    h2 {
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }

    h3 {
      font-size: var(--fs-lg);
      font-weight: var(--fw-bold);
      color: var(--clr-primary-400);
      margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    }

    p {
      color: var(--clr-neutral-300);
    }

    .content {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 55% 45%;
    }

    .image {
      display: grid;
      place-items: center;
    }

    .image img {
      height: 200px;
      aspect-ratio: 1;
      object-fit: cover;
      border-radius: 50%;
      border: 4px solid var(--clr-primary-400);
    }

    @media (max-width: 913px) {
      .content {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
        gap: 2rem;
      }

      h2,
      h3,
      p {
        text-align: center;
      }

      .image {
        order: -1;
      }
    }
  </style>
</section>
